SYNOPSIS:

    ghmtools <operation> [<option>...] [--] <argument>...
        execute a given operation with given options and arguments

    ghmtools help
        display a list of operations

    ghmtools help <operation>
        display the help message for a given operation

OPERATIONS:

    analysis
        create gene activity files from RNA-seq data, ChIP-seq data, and bound
        bound gene lists

    heatmap
        create gene transcription and gene binding heatmaps from gene activity
        files
